name: en-osm_viewer_v3_cameroon
title: World Maps & Satellite Photos
description:
Search for cities/towns with more than 1000 people. There are about 127,654 worldwide:

  • Worldwide satellite photos: 10 levels of zoom (305-metre resolution)
  • Cameroon satellite photos: 13 levels of zoom (19-metre resolution)
  • Worldwide maps: 15 levels of zoom + 4 levels of overzoom to highlight building details and natural geography
extra_description: Thank you to the OpenStreetMap community, making it possible for anybody to improve these maps for the benefit of all.
